      <title>罗马尼亚和保加利亚获得免护照欧盟区全面准入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/romania-and-bulgaria-win-full-access-to-passport-free-eu-area</link>
      <description><![CDATA[经过近二十年的艰苦努力，罗马尼亚和保加利亚将于明年完全获得进入欧盟免护照区的资格，这将有助于提振这两个国家陷入困境的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/romania-and-bulgaria-win-full-access-to-passport-free-eu-area</guid>
