    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据称华宝即将收购联合信托银行少数股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/warburg-is-said-to-near-deal-for-united-trust-bank-minority-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，华平投资集团 (Warburg Pincus) 正就收购联合信托银行 (United Trust Bank) 20% 的股份进行深入谈判，此举将使这家英国专业贷款机构的估值达到约 5 亿英镑（6.38 亿美元）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-12/warburg-is-said-to-near-deal-for-united-trust-bank-minority-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 08:35:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
